00:03:12.639 --> 00:03:14.759
Right now, a document written
by the Grand Princess

00:03:16.080 --> 00:03:17.599
should be reaching Grand Tutor Xie.

00:03:18.840 --> 00:03:20.352
Write another letter

00:03:20.352 --> 00:03:21.560
in the Grand Princess's hand.

00:03:24.120 --> 00:03:25.240
And in her name,

00:03:25.719 --> 00:03:28.159
accuse the Xie family
of colluding, harming loyal subjects,

00:03:28.224 --> 00:03:29.568
and killing the Grand Princess.

