00:05:45.279 --> 00:05:46.639
and marry me in the palace,

00:05:47.240 --> 00:05:48.959
this joyful union between families

00:05:49.439 --> 00:05:50.839
could warrant a general pardon.

00:05:52.519 --> 00:05:53.480
