00:06:59.279 --> 00:07:01.720
I only wanted
to find a scapegoat for you.

00:07:02.680 --> 00:07:04.399
I can bring you into the harem.

00:07:04.680 --> 00:07:06.680
I can give you a new identity.

00:07:06.839 --> 00:07:08.959
