00:07:10.079 --> 00:07:11.040
Sheng Yunlin,

00:07:12.920 --> 00:07:14.800
I was the first to fall for you.

00:07:15.879 --> 00:07:17.800
I was the one who stayed
by your side all along.

00:07:18.319 --> 00:07:20.560
